description: The 12-Channel Adjustable Pipette, 5-50 µL, BRAND is the perfect manual pipette for demanding laboratory scientists with intensive ergonomic and innovative materials. It offers robust yet lightweight construction, superior autoclavability, one-handed operation, high degree of accuracy and precision and long lasting reliability. This pipette can be applied for research, diagnotic, and clinical pipetting.
name: S 12-Channel Adjustable Pipette
